{"title":"改造旧城一角  录像","authors":["梁志宏"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":3,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"改造旧城一角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"录像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁志宏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早春。一场机械强台风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰隆隆，从旧城一角卷过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷过斑驳的明砖清瓦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷过嘈杂的深巷陋院"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷过爆起的欣喜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及疑虑、埋怨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揭去大城市一块残破的补丁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片暂时的废墟之上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝图，沉重地溅落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望，抢时播种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎下一百根承重桩一百根信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爆出一万束钢筋丛一万束憧憬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水和阳光猛烈浇灌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住宅建筑群猛烈拔节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市风景线，在这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向一个新的层次上升"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪耀大片大片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红玛瑙蓝玻璃白水晶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪耀亮晶晶的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮晶晶的笑容"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}